ed States took the bronze with 298kg.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.9999997930096002, \"rank\": 1.2375602685070277e-07, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\", \"score\": 0.9954139269228617, \"rank\": 0.0037544072389597413, \"text\": \"Hampton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"score\": 0.6073525701135758, \"rank\": 0.6446268420683212, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morris_Motors\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999850415972876, \"rank\": 0.00014547680735011744, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Cover image via CFP)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/College_Football_Playoff\", \"score\": 0.9194787535441716, \"ra